{
  "number": 70,
  "name": "سُورَةُ المَعَارِجِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Ma'aarij",
  "englishNameTranslation": "The Ascending Stairways",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 5376,
      "text": "ONE who is minded to ask might ask about the suffering which [in the hereafter] is bound to befall",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5377,
      "text": "those who deny the truth. [Know, then, that] nothing can ward it off,",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5378,
      "text": "[since it will come] from God, unto whom there are many ways of ascent:",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5379,
      "text": "all the angels and all the inspiration [ever granted to man] ascend unto Him [daily,] in a day the length whereof is [like] fifty thousand years…",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5380,
      "text": "Therefore, [O believer,] endure all adversity with goodly patience:",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5381,
      "text": "behold, men look upon that [reckoning] as something far away –",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5382,
      "text": "but, We see it as near!",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5383,
      "text": "[It will take place] on a Day when the sky will be like molten lead,",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5384,
      "text": "and the mountains will be like tufts of wool,",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5385,
      "text": "and [when] no friend will ask about his friend,",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5386,
      "text": "though they may be in one another's sight: [for,] everyone who was lost in sin will on that Day but desire to ransom himself from suffering at the price of his own children,",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5387,
      "text": "and of his spouse, and of his brother,",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5388,
      "text": "and of all the kinsfolk who ever sheltered him,",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5389,
      "text": "and of whoever [else] lives on earth, all of them - so that he could but save himself.",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5390,
      "text": "But nay! Verily, all [that awaits him] is a raging flame,",
      "numberInSurah": 15,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5391,
      "text": "tearing away his skin!",
      "numberInSurah": 16,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5392,
      "text": "It will claim all such as turn their backs [on what is right], and turn away [from the truth],",
      "numberInSurah": 17,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5393,
      "text": "and amass [wealth] and thereupon withhold [it from their fellow-men].",
      "numberInSurah": 18,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5394,
      "text": "VERILY, man is born with a restless disposition.",
      "numberInSurah": 19,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5395,
      "text": "[As a rule,] whenever misfortune touches him, he is filled with self-pity;",
      "numberInSurah": 20,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5396,
      "text": "and whenever good fortune comes to him, he selfishly withholds it [from others].",
      "numberInSurah": 21,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5397,
      "text": "Not so, however, those who consciously turn towards God in prayer.",
      "numberInSurah": 22,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5398,
      "text": "[and] who incessantly persevere in their prayer",
      "numberInSurah": 23,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5399,
      "text": "and in whose possessions there is a due share, acknowledged [by them],",
      "numberInSurah": 24,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5400,
      "text": "for such as ask [for help] and such as are deprived [of what is good in life];",
      "numberInSurah": 25,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5401,
      "text": "and who accept as true the [coming of the] Day of Judgment;",
      "numberInSurah": 26,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5402,
      "text": "and who stand in dread of their Sustainer's chastisement –",
      "numberInSurah": 27,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5403,
      "text": "for, behold, of their Sustainer's chastisement none may ever feel [wholly] secure;",
      "numberInSurah": 28,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5404,
      "text": "and who are mindful of their chastity,",
      "numberInSurah": 29,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5405,
      "text": "[not giving way to their desires] with any but their spouses - that is, those whom they rightfully possess [through wedlock] -: for then, behold, they are free of all blame,",
      "numberInSurah": 30,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5406,
      "text": "whereas such as seek to go beyond that [limit] are truly transgressors;",
      "numberInSurah": 31,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5407,
      "text": "and who are faithful to their trusts and to their pledges:",
      "numberInSurah": 32,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5408,
      "text": "and who stand firm whenever they bear witness;",
      "numberInSurah": 33,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5409,
      "text": "and who guard their prayers [from all worldly intent].",
      "numberInSurah": 34,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5410,
      "text": "These it is who in the gardens [of paradise] shall be honoured!",
      "numberInSurah": 35,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5411,
      "text": "WHAT, THEN, is amiss with such as are bent on denying the truth, that they run about confusedly to and fro before thee,",
      "numberInSurah": 36,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5412,
      "text": "[coming upon thee] from the right and from the left, in crowds?",
      "numberInSurah": 37,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5413,
      "text": "Does every one of them hope to enter [by this means] a garden of bliss?",
      "numberInSurah": 38,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5414,
      "text": "Never! For, behold, We have created them out of something that they know [only too well]!",
      "numberInSurah": 39,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5415,
      "text": "But nay! I call to witness [Our being] the Sustainer of all the points of sunrise and sunset: verily, well able are We",
      "numberInSurah": 40,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5416,
      "text": "to replace them with [people] better than they are; for there is nothing to prevent Us [from doing what We will].",
      "numberInSurah": 41,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5417,
      "text": "Hence, leave them to indulge in idle talk and play [with words] until they face that [Judgment] Day of theirs which they have been promised –",
      "numberInSurah": 42,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5418,
      "text": "the Day when they shall come forth in haste from their graves, as if racing towards a goal-post,",
      "numberInSurah": 43,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5419,
      "text": "with downcast eyes, with ignominy overwhelming them: that Day which they were promised again and…",
      "numberInSurah": 44,
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ],
